            <div class="overview-text">
                <h1 class="section-title" style="font-size: 2.8em;">Overview</h1>
                <p class="overview-content">Our system is built to handle elections of all sizes, from small community
                    votes to large-scale
                     for Universities. With ElectionHub, you can vote from the comfort of your
                    home or
                    anywhere with internet access, ensuring that every vote is counted accurately and fairly.</p>

