            <div class="card-number">1</div>
            <h3>Security</h3>
            <p>State-of-the-art encryption and security measures to protect voter information and prevent
                fraud.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">Top Priority</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-number">2</div>
            <h3>Accessibility</h3>
            <p>Easy-to-use interface accessible from any device with internet connectivity.</p>
