    <div id="How to Vote" class="section">
        <h1 class="section-title" style="font-size: 2em;padding-left: 472px;">How it Works</h1>
        <h4 style="font-size: 1.4em;">below is Step by Step guide to participate in Elections</h4>
        <div class="cards">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-number">1</div>
                <h3>Get Started</h3>
                <p>Create your account with a valid email address.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">Takes a few seconds</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-number">2</div>
                <h3>Verify Email</h3>
                <p>Check your email for the verification link and verify your account.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">Takes 1 min</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-number">3</div>
                <h3>Log In</h3>
                <p>Log in with your credentials.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">Takes a few seconds</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-number">4</div>
                <h3>Registered as a Voter</h3>
                <p>Register as a voter to access the voting dashboard.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">Takes a 2 minutes</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-number">5</div>
                <h3>Select Election Poll</h3>
                <p>Choose the election you want to participate in from the list.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">Takes 1 min</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-number">6</div>
                <h3>Select Position</h3>
                <p>Choose the Position from the list.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">Takes 1 min</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-number">6</div>
                <h3>Cast Your Vote</h3>
                <p>Make your selections, review them, and submit your vote.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">Takes a few minutes</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-number">7</div>
                <h3>Confirm Submission</h3>
                <p>Receive a confirmation message that your vote has been recorded.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">Instant</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-number">8</div>
                <h3>View results</h3>
                <p>finally you can see the outcomes of voting.</p>
                <div class="card-footer">Takes 2 hours</div>
            </div>
        </div>
