    <div id="Eligibility" class="section">
        <div class="overview-content">
            <div class="overview-image">
                <img src="/Public/images/img6.png" alt="Voting Image">
            </div>
            <div class="overview-text">
                <h1 class="section-title" style="font-size: 2.8em;padding-left: 50px;">Who Is Eligible</h1>
                <p class="overview-content">To be eligible to vote in University elections using our online voting
                    system, you must meet the following criteria:</p>
                <ul class="eligibility-list">
                    <li>Be a  Regular Student in University.</li>
                    <li>Hold a valid Computerized National Identity Card (CNIC).</li>
                    <li>Ensure your email address and mobile number are up to date.</li>
                    <li>Voter must be above 18 to cast vote.</li>
                    <li>Follow any additional requirements set by the University.</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="eligibility-note">Please check with the following University for specific
                    eligibility requirements and ensure all your information is accurate and up to date.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
